			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left or Right Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire special weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire heavy weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire gun:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump / Brake (hovercar):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Action:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change target:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Transform to hovercar or walker:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 + R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jink left or right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Short jink left or right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 + L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Crouch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 + Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
